questions.quote: And I had won by so much a myth began to grow about my speed. Only Duncan suspected something was a miss. He's hated me ever since. Now he's back.
I'm with people, I'll be with you in a moment.  So, you want a protein shake, or something?
Your son could never afford that car. We all saw his act, last year, at the playhouse. He's lucky he can pay his rent!
It's all in your head. All she knows is she had a good time. I think you should call her.
Yeah, he's a hoot.  Oh, goodbye, my dear.    Ouch.    Weekend of the 26th, come on out, we're having another party.
Well, how do you think I feel? Instead of editing the first novel of a major young writing talent, I am proofreading a food allergy cookbook.
Oh! Jeez! Well, you've got a maid. It's a whole different world downtown-- different Gap, different Tower Records, and she's a 646.
Alright, what's the difference. What are we gonna do now? He won't take our calls, we can't get into his office...
No, we can't. My skin is crawling just being inside your little rat's nest. Now, what happened?
So yesterday, after they took you away, I looked in my mail and I noticed that the mailman accidentally put your Visa renewal in my mail box.
